#
# This is a sample "scnhosts" file used by "RSCnet.dll for RICOH Scanner Driver"
# for Network Scanner producted by RICOH.
#
# This file contains the mappings of IP addresses to Network Scanner. Each entry
# should be kept on an individual line. All numbers supplied as parts in a '.' notation must be decimal.
# The "#" character is generally used to denote the start of a comment.
#
# If you want to use Network Scanner in the different segment, Please write the
# IP addresses of the Network Scanner in "scnhosts". "RSCnet.dll for RICOH Scanner Driver"
# refer only the IP address written in "scnhosts", can browse Network Scanner in the different segment.
#
# For example
# IP address      
# 111.111.111.111 
# 222.222.222.222 
#


